## What happens next

1. You reply with approve/reject decisions.
2. The agent downloads each approved URL (up to 3 retries per URL).
3. The agent uploads documents to the knowledge base and triggers `run_document` to start ingestion.
4. The agent **pauses again** after upload and asks you to send `resume` when you are ready for the ingestion-verification check.

See [`src/SKILL.md`](../../SKILL.md) §7 for the full pause/resume protocol.
